metadata.name: Noodle Portrait 001 - Monoline Monroe v1/4
metadata.description:
I am proud to present Monoline Monroe as my inaugural design to kick off my Noodle Portrait collection. 

I am line artist Tyler Foust. My specialty is complex one line drawings that create an illusion of chaos up close but then become organized and clear from a distance. 

Each Noodle Portrait is originally hand drawn with ink on paper using one line that never intersects. 

Each week for the next 52 weeks I will release 1 new Noodle Portrait with 4 variations.
